## Packet Reference

### Tuya serial frame format
```
55 AA [ver] [cmd] [len_h] [len_l] [data...] [checksum]
```

| Field | Value | Notes |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Header | 55 AA | Always |
| Version | 00 | Module→MCU direction |
| Cmd | 06 | SetDP (module pushing to MCU) |
| Cmd | 07 | State (MCU reporting to module) |
| Checksum | sum of all bytes mod 256 | |

### Study mode ON
```
55 AA 00 06 00 05 01 04 00 01 01 11
```

### Study mode OFF
```
55 AA 00 06 00 05 01 04 00 01 02 12
```

### Heartbeat
```
55 AA 00 00 00 00 FF
```

### Send IR code (DP7, 80 bytes example)
```
55 AA 00 06 00 54 07 00 00 50 [80 bytes of IR code] [checksum]
```

